SUMMARY:We the Future 2026 Conference
DESCRIPTION:We are excited to share that the selected Keynote Speaker is 
 Prisca Dorcas Mojica RodrûÙguez. (https://www.priscadorcas.com/bio/) Pris
 ca Dorcas Mojica Rodriguez is a writer\, organizer\, and public intellect
 ual whose work centers on the lived experiences of undocumented and forme
 rly undocumented Latine communities. Through powerful storytelling and in
 cisive cultural critique\, she challenges dominant narratives about immig
 ration\, belonging\, and identity in the United States.  Tell us you are 
 coming by submitting your RSVP here (https://santarosajuniorcollege.forms
 tack.com/forms/form_1__we_the_future_registration_2026)!  For more inform
 ation\, visit SRJC's We the Future Website (https://wethefuture.santarosa
 .edu/)!
X-ALT-DESC;FMTTYPE=text/html:<p>  We are excited to share that the select
 ed Keynote Speaker is <a href="https://www.priscadorcas.com/bio/">Prisca 
 Dorcas Mojica RodrûÙguez.</a> Prisca Dorcas Mojica Rodriguez is a writer\
 , organizer\, and public intellectual whose work centers on the lived exp
 eriences of undocumented and formerly undocumented Latine communities. Th
 rough powerful storytelling and incisive cultural critique\, she challeng
 es dominant narratives about immigration\, belonging\, and identity in th
 e United States.</p><p>  Tell us you are coming by submitting your <a hre
 f="https://santarosajuniorcollege.formstack.com/forms/form_1__we_the_futu
 re_registration_2026" target="_blank" rel="noopener">RSVP here</a>!</p><p
